Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:19.59,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Gust of wind leaves fall leaves falling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:17.04,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:22.11,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That was big!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.11,0:00:24.08,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I moved so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:26.00,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Not as fast as Chihaya though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:28.45,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,She's not even watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:34.16,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan and Desktomu-kun are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:36.51,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,pretty even in terms of reflexes and speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:39.01,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:43.10,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,one of them is pulling ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:56.78,Chiha-title,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1700,0)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:06.14,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1000)}Verse 19
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:06.14,Chiha-ep-title-poem,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1000)}As \Nthe\N Years\N Pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:13.61,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun has two faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:15.64,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan has zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:21.53,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Those faults give Kana-chan \Na two card lead by default.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:26.04,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I've always believed that \Nyou can make up for faults,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:30.04,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,but after playing Kanai Sakura-san, \NI realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:33.00,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Faults can be fatal when you're playing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.25,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,an opponent who doesn't make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:40.54,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving up more than just a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:42.48,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You lose your cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:46.01,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Two faults against Kana-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:47.83,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.  Really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:49.52,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I need to make up those cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:51.62,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You lose your rhythm,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:54.52,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,while allowing your opponent to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:59.03,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,His two faults have done more \Nthan cost him two cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:05.73,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,As this trip takes me away in haste,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:03.10,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Good, I finally took a card \Nfrom the opponent's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:05.46,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,A comeback!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:08.87,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Time to stage a comeback!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:09.74,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.13,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:17.13,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,for I could not recognize you,\N like the moon hidden behind the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:17.13,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,This is a one-syllable card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:19.67,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I sent the wrong card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.27,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:23.98,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I've never sent a \None-syllable card before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:26.62,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,First, I commit faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.61,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm sending the wrong cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:31.23,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I keep screwing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:34.23,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I'm playing against
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.32,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan and myself at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:39.63,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen him do this in practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.03,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,When Desktomu-kun is losing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:44.11,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,near the end of a match, \Nhe tends to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.66,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,and look ahead to his next chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:49.28,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,The match is almost over \Nand I'm down 8 cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:51.27,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:55.10,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm down 8 cards.  Down 8 cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:58.15,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the final.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:01.42,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,There is no next chance, Desktomu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:19.69,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We can train ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:23.01,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,So we can focus when we're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:26.32,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,So we're able to play \Nten hours straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:31.62,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:33.72,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to move my cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:34.62,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:35.64,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.26,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:43.48,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is that allowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.57,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen people move cards
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:47.10,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,together when they only have four left,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.89,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,but he still has ten cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.02,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,That was a bold move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.18,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,If she has two cards left \Nand I have ten left,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:05:00.98,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,have only autumn leaves as an offering \Nfor the gods watching over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:56.49,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,there's a higher probability that one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:58.44,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,of my cards will be read.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:04.26,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,So spring ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.95,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,I know that my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:08.91,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,He's hitting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.29,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,All of the cards on his side!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:19.87,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to gamble on \Nhis cards being read?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:22.22,Chiha-internal,B,0000,0000,0000,,That's reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.85,Chiha-internal,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cheering for the girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.01,Chiha-internal,B,0000,0000,0000,,Attack his side!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.78,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I have a six card lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:36.06,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,and by no fault of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:30.12,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:32.27,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,When his cards are all grouped together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.06,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,it's easier for me to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.63,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in good shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:44.05,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Long last we meet,\N only for me to leave hurriedly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:42.90,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's the one-syllable card he just sent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:48.23,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun was dead set \Non taking that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:48.97,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,for I could not recognize you,\N like the moon hidden behind the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:55.16,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose to Kana-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:57.67,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,but I definitely
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.17,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,don't want to lose to myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:04.09,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I have a five card lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.91,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:10.32,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.95,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun is hitting all of \Nhis cards at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:15.68,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,but I still have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:19.54,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to reach straight \Nfor the correct card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:21.69,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Straight and swift...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:25.26,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Play on the edge, the way Chihaya-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:26.78,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,did against the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:30.20,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the beating of cloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.20,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's too hard without \Nany preparation first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:35.74,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:43.22,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Impassionate gods have never seen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:38.69,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,the red that is the Tatsuta River\Nare joined at river's end
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:44.21,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Kana-chan was so \Nfast on "Impassionate"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:49.45,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun was
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.85,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,looking at the "Impassioned"\Ncard on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.20,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,until the day waves crash over Mount Suenomatsu\Ncovered by the smoky mountain fog
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.35,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like how Desktomu-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:58.96,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,the red that is the Tatsuta River
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:58.62,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,took "While it pains" from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:03.72,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten better at the \Ncards my friends are good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:07.17,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,One more card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:09.81,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,One more card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:12.99,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.76,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The storm will soon carry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:15.57,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.87,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,A night spent waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:17.87,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.69,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.87,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody wishes to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:37.87,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,covered by the smoky mountain fog
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:48.90,Chiha-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:55.41,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:10.85,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan, congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:26.69,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan, your swing is too big!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:28.94,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't using the form I taught you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:31.19,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun, you should use \Na thrust for that card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:32.88,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Stay focused!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:44.96,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:46.85,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:51.70,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You came in first.  You came in second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:53.88,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That's incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.56,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.66,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:12.23,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I completely forgot about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:13.90,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Retro-kun, Retro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.56,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Give me an update.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:16.11,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:28.83,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}long as the nights I spend alone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.01,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Luck of the draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:40.46,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,When each player only has one card left
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.21,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,and they play defensively,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:45.74,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,the match comes down to \Nwhose card is read first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:47.94,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Pure luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:52.24,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,So the final ends in luck of the draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.84,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching this match to \Nsee if I could learn anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:58.20,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,but in terms of reflexes, \Nspeed, and memorization,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.02,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm clearly better than both of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:03.20,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing for me to learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:05.78,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:07.83,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,After all they've been through,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.12,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,the winner will be determined by luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:12.07,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,They worked so hard to get here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:15.04,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,"The tail"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.06,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Give me "The tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:19.31,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Give me "The tail"!  \NGive it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:22.47,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defend this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:27.48,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Focus.  Reassess the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.51,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I have "Swift waters"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:32.60,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,A one-syllable card on "Swift."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.78,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Nishida has "The tail,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:38.52,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,and six dead cards \Nhaven't been read yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.75,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,"The sky may," "The sight \Nof Mount," "Feel sorrow,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:43.99,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,"For the," "Would this," and "My own sleeves."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:48.50,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,"The tail" can't be taken on \Nthe first syllable yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:55.28,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The sky may hold the same moon
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:57.26,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,H-He went on the attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:10:58.53,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:00.97,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,take the opponent's card \Nin a luck of the draw?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:04.44,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to protect \Nyour own card, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:05.51,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:10.50,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't there two of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:16.31,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't I watch this \Nimportant match?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:20.27,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Luck of the draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:21.48,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.75,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not leaving this match
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:25.50,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,to luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:28.04,Toda,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Toda Municipal Spor
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.04,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Luck of the draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.99,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Each player only has one card left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.34,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If both players try to \Ndefend their own card,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:42.27,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,they each have a 50% chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:47.14,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But Taichi is trying to improve \Nhis chances of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.64,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,By attacking the opponent's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.31,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to luck of the draw,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.75,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,it's normal to defend your own card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.25,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,It's the golden rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:58.29,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,However, Mashima went on the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:01.25,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,His card is "Swift," a one-syllable card.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:03.66,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,So the question is:\N are there any other
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:06.17,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,"The" cards left besides "The tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:09.02,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Think...  Think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:11.01,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Were they all read?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.27,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Are there a few left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:13.43,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:16.32,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,There are sixteen "The" cards in total...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:22.05,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,There are definitely other cards left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:24.36,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to attack again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:37.02,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,which shines over Mount Mikasa
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:44.93,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Feel sorrow wash over \Nme when I see the moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:55.19,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,though autumn is not mine alone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:13:04.20,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,My own sleeves are like the sands \Nat the edge of the ebbing tide,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:11.68,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Would this old palace courtyard \Nand the eaves strewn with weeds
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.79,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Another dead card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:11.26,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,They're running out of cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:14.95,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,The intensity when each card is read
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:17.34,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,is similar to when sumo \Nwrestlers face off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:20.53,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,Focus, then relax. \N Focus, then relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:22.74,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't moved an inch,\N yet you feel completely drained.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.32,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it when you get a bunch \Nof dead cards in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:29.03,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,Just read one of the \Ntwo remaining cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:41.85,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't relaxing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.66,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,Because they care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.84,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}are joined at river's end
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.43,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,Because they want to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:14:00.61,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,be as dear now, \Nthose were the good old days
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:07.43,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The sight of Mount Arima with the bamboo \Nleaves fading across the plains
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:05.86,Chiha-internal,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Another dead card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:08.45,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But "The sight of Mount" has been read!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:15.37,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,So there was still a "The" card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:18.76,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,But that should be all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:21.03,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,It comes down to whether \N"Swift" or "The" is read.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:22.38,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,A 50/50 battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.94,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, there's another one left?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:31.25,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:34.24,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Would you able to hear the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:36.68,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,sound that comes before "The"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:39.26,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,The sound that comes before "Swift"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:47.27,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,makes me wonder how I ever \Nlet you fade from my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:42.90,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:45.13,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:53.24,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The tail feathers of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.89,0:15:08.76,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,long as the nights I spend alone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.28,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:30.82,Toda,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Toda Municipal Sports Center
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:36.98,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be waiting in the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:39.08,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:46.37,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Nishida, did you know \Nwhich cards were left?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:50.35,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, wasn't {\i1}Swift{\i0} the only card left?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:51.59,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Swift{\i0} and {\i1}For the{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.93,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.85,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Mashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:02.15,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:03.34,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:17.72,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for me to blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:18.97,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:24.38,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't lose because of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:28.88,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault for not winning \Nbefore it got to that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:32.51,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,There were plenty of cards I should \Nhave gotten in the first half!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:35.84,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Nishida was able to fend \Noff my weak attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.85,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Nishida did a better job of protecting \Nhis multi-syllable cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:43.73,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,There was plenty of \Nroom for improvement!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.09,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:49.95,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I tried my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.33,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,But that's no excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:10.75,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:13.69,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.  Taichi.  Porky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:16.64,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're president \Nof the karuta club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:20.67,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.64,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.80,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:25.85,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,compared to Ayase,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:29.51,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,who gives people weird nicknames \Nlike Porky and Desktomu,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:34.50,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,and she's such an airhead	 that \Nwe let her get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:45.75,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one \Nwho calls me Nishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:49.37,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep playing karuta with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:17:59.68,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:01.43,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.00,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't forget anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.18,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.04,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.58,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:08.69,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna grab something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:16.69,van,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Oe Traditional Clothing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:16.70,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for driving us home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:18.45,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:21.24,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the Mizusawa \NKaruta Club did great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:23.32,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Four of the five members placed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:25.52,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and three members advanced in rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:28.78,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:29.83,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:33.74,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The top three finalists in \NClass D advance to Class C,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:35.72,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,so both Kana-chan and Desk-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.23,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Komano-kun get to advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:38.24,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Komano-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:39.84,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone worked really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:43.48,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe that I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:45.05,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.93,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I was really amazed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:50.49,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,In your match against Desk- Komano-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:53.61,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell that you've \Nreally improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:56.86,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You were taking cards without making a sound, \Nwithout using too much force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:00.66,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:03.15,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,What?  You've done it \Nbefore, Chihaya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:03.53,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:07.34,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,The last card you took in \Nthe finals against Hokuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:08.66,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I can still remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:11.74,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:12.75,Chiha-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.67,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:17.71,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hard to be relaxed \Nwhile taking a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:19.14,Chiha-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:20.68,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:28.18,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that I was playing \N120% in the finals today,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:32.90,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,but that was because I was \Nplaying against Desktomu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:33.61,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:35.34,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't so much worried
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.41,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,about winning as I was focused
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:39.25,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,on playing my style of karuta,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:40.86,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,so I didn't feel any pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:45.76,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.44,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Pressure, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:03.47,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi and I are always under pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:06.76,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play a team match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:13.36,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play as a team again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:21.35,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Our team is a lot stronger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:24.28,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Two Class A players, one Class \NB player, two Class C players.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:26.17,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:30.52,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.  That means I might run into Pork-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.41,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nishida-kun at the next tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:35.02,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase, you've been acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:36.16,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:38.80,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!  You must have heard what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.80,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Er, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.93,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.  You're supposed \Nto be an airhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:44.80,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't feel right otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:45.70,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.93,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You've helped me learn \Na valuable lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:51.81,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I have no expectations of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:49.78,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,My team.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:53.66,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That's very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.71,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:20:59.40,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:03.26,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,The results for the Saitama \Ntournament last weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:06.88,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Our Murao-kun was there, \Nand he placed third in Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:08.70,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,The Kanto region is competitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.69,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted some \Nmore time to think it over,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:15.01,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,but have you made a decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:17.04,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Count me in,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:20.04,List,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Class B\NWinner     Nishida Yusei\NRunner-up  Mashima Taichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:20.60,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,for the west Master qualifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:24.84,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aiming to be the Western finalist.
